              <h2>What are case studies?</h2>
              <p>Climate-ADAPT case studies showcase initiatives that are already being carried out in Europe to adapt to climate change and increase resilience to extreme weather and slow-onset events. </p>
              <p>Case studies are flagship of the Climate-ADAPT platform. They have a comprehensive structure that covers all the key aspects in the implementation cycle of adaptation measures and are careful and specifically prepared for Climate-ADAPT by the organisation that is involved in the implementation with the support of EEA, following a set of <a href="https://climate-adapt.eea.europa.eu/repository/11090223.pdf">criteria</a> and also in collaboration with the main stakeholders.</p>
